{"id":125823,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/金正恩要“反腐败”还是要大清洗？/","date":"2010-11-26T03:58:30Z","modified":"2010-11-26T03:58:30Z","title":"金正恩要“反腐败”还是要大清洗？","content":"<p><p align=\"left\"><span>据韩国《朝鲜日报》日前援引韩国一个对朝民间团体的消息称，最近朝鲜开始采取措施大力整治干部腐败问题。报道称，在朝鲜劳动党军事委员会副委员长金正恩的主导下，朝鲜对全国范围的腐败干部进行大规模审查，被揭发的干部多隶属于朝鲜总管边防部队和保安机关。报道援引一名朝鲜消息人士的话称，<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>日开始，朝鲜咸镜北道党组织和监察委员会用一周时间对茂山郡进行了集中监察，逮捕了<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>名涉嫌默许民众叛逃和接受贿赂的朝鲜劳动党及保安部门的干部。一时间，</span><span>金正恩在朝鲜“反腐败”的名声鹊起。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span>不过，金正恩在朝鲜真是在“反腐败”吗？假设金正恩在朝鲜真是在“反腐败”，金正恩能够将“反腐败”进行下去吗？！这是人们值得质疑的大问题。</span></p>\n<p><span>假设 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}